Warning: Don't upgrade a version 2 system to version 3 before you have
read the instructions in doc/UPGRADE!

The branches are:
- master: the unmodified SQL-Ledger from sql-ledger.com with version tags

- full: the master branch with additions by Tekki: security patch for
  template editor, WLprinter, Swiss German, French and Italian charts
  of accounts, updated languages, full UTF-8 support.
  To use WLprinter, add a printer with command "wlprinter".

